27/07/2008
TIRANA, Albania -- Brigadier General Maksim Malaj was appointed as the new chief of the Albanian General Staff on Friday (July 25th).
He replaces General Luan Hoxha, who was dismissed on June 16th following a series of deadly explosions in March at an ammunitions depot in Gerdec that killed 26 people and injured more than 300.
(MIA, Makfax - 25/07/08)
